description:
Hello, I'm Agatha! 😊

In today's video, I'm going to share with you another makeup comparison review! It's going to be a review about moisturizing and hydrating tints. I featured products from sunnies face, happy skin, strokes beauty lab, and vice cosmetics. I hope this video will help you in choosing which product to buy 🥰

If you have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise) 

Products mentioned:
SUNNIES FACE LIP TREAT IN JUICE
https://www.lazada.com.ph/products/sunnies-face-lip-treat-moisturizing-tinted-lip-balm-juice-i1254348834-s4511604068.html?spm=a2o4l.searchlist.list.1.40fa5b35BX1Q63&search=1

GENERATION HAPPY SKIN KISS AND BLOOM TINT IN CRIMSON
https://shopee.ph/Happy-Skin-Kiss-Bloom-Glossy-Tint-in-Crimson-i.85793610.7343242000

STROKES BEAUTY LAB SILK KISS IN PASSIONATE PEACH
https://shopee.ph/Strokes-Silk-Kiss-in-Passionate-Peach-Lip-Oil--i.289919484.3176416190

VICE CO. BT21 DEWY TINT IN FRESH NUDE
https://shopee.ph/BT21-Dewy-Tint-Fresh-Nude-i.53860691.4144139974 

Let's be friends!
